net.sourceforge.cilib.Container.Graph
Class Edge

java.lang.Object
  net.sourceforge.cilib.Container.Graph.Edge
public class Edge
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents an edge connecting two Vertex nodes in a Graph The Edge can be a uni-directional and well as a bi-directional edge.

Author:
Gary Pampara

addVertexInformation

public void addVertexInformation(boolean bidirectional)
Add the needed information about the vertex to the Vertices. This call is implicitly handled by the Graph and DirectedGraph with addEdge(Edge)

Parameters:
bidirectional - It true the edge is an edge on an undirected graph, if false it is the edge on a directed graph.
See Also:
